/* Request for Deletion of Inaccurate Mauryan Empire Map on Wikipedia */ new section

The deletion of a distorted Mauryan Empire map from a Wiki page is justified due to its lack of authenticity, absence of endorsement by the Indian Archaeological Survey of India, exclusion from Indian history textbooks, and potential to spread misinformation. The inaccurate representation of territorial boundaries and historical events raises concerns about its reliability.Maintaining scholarly integrity and avoiding bias are paramount on Wiki pages.
